  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a simple and very addictive multiplayer game where you can fight tank battles with your friends, acquaintances and strangers. You appear on the battlefield and immediately start participating in a tank battle. All you have to do is collect ammunition, dodge shots, and of course, destroy as many enemy tanks as possible. You get one point for hitting a tank. If you are beaten, one point is taken away. Try not to go into negative territory.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a simple and very addictive multiplayer game where you can fight tank battles with your friends, acquaintances and strangers. You appear on the battlefield and immediately start participating in a tank battle. All you have to do is collect ammunition, dodge shots, and of course, destroy as many enemy tanks as possible. You get one point for hitting a tank. If you are beaten, one point is taken away. Try not to go into negative territory.</p>",
